ArtyTorrent Pack 49-Electro Drum Loops 110-119 bpm-WAV samples
--------------------------------------------------------------

A selection of electro beats, primarily with that old skool flavour, due to the use of the TR-808 drum machine. Useful for modern electro house, hip hop and mash-up breaks. It&#039;s block party time!

Tempo ranges from 110-119 bpm.

Torrent contains 4 RAR files with 71 loops.
-------------------------------------------
Chicago Fire Electro 110-119 (11 loops)
Designer Dance Tools El Breaks 112-116 (7 loops)
Electro 115 (10 loops)
Misc Electro 110-119 (43 loops)

All samples have been normalized and acidized and are 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz, looped precisely and containing the approx bpm in the filenames.

The samples are from a variety of sources including CDs produced by East-West, Sonic Foundry/Sony, and Syntrillium/Loopology.
